				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This is the main hag dialogue. In it, you can ask about Mayrina (who is present) or make a deal to have your parasite removed. \r\n\r\nIf you keep asking about Mayrina (twice), the hag will be furious and vanish Mayrina away while she deals with the 'busybody' - the player.\r\n\r\nIf you agree to the tadpole deal, you must give up an eye (in the transformed dialogue)."
				}
			}
